## CSV Example

  ```shell
  curl "<%= config[:apihost] %>/data-browser-api/view/csv?states=CA,MD,DC&years=2018&actions_taken=5"
  ```

  ```GET``` CSV file with the following parameters

  var | value
  --- | ---
  states | CA, MD, DC
  years | 2018
  action_taken | 5

